stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> IDLE

    IDLE --> WAIT_BANK_GNTS: wants_refresh<br/>(postponer fired)

    WAIT_BANK_GNTS --> DO_REFRESH: all bank_machines<br/>asserted refresh_gnt

    DO_REFRESH --> CHECK_ZQCS: refresh sequencer done<br/>(N refreshes issued)

    CHECK_ZQCS --> DO_ZQCS: wants_zqcs<br/>(zqcs timer fired)
    CHECK_ZQCS --> RELEASE: zqcs not due

    DO_ZQCS --> RELEASE: ZQCS executer done

    RELEASE --> IDLE: deassert refresh_req<br/>(banks can leave REFRESHING)

    note right of DO_REFRESH
      Sequencer issues N
      back-to-back PRE_ALL +
      AUTO_REF commands
      (deterministic batching)
    end note

    note right of DO_ZQCS
      Piggybacked on refresh:
      reuses 'all banks idle'
      guarantee, no separate
      bus-blocking event
    end note
